{"tid":1828535,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"陳帆：按公屋編排優次決定 非懲罰年輕人","createTime":"2020-01-18T02:57:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-18T16:06:39.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":43,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"9a1e0a84afc63a94eac7f8a2c4a7cff8796ce362","tid":1828535,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T02:57:59.000Z","msg":"政府建議向輪候公屋滿三年，而沒領取綜援的人提供現金津貼，但不包括非長者單身人士。運輸及房屋局局長陳帆出席本台節問《星期六問責》時，否認做法是懲罰年輕人，只是按一向的公屋編排優次，決定資助對象。<br />\n<br />\n被問到單身年輕人輪候公屋的時間，相對家庭及長者長，為何反而沒現金津貼補助，陳帆指政策發展至今有其理由，又指年輕人大多與家人同住，本身已有居所，只是長大後希望有自己「小天地」。"},{"pid":"72ecc331c02e303668197faefaf77ef54791125b","tid":1828535,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T02:58:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1503483-20200118.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1503483-20200118.htm&d=qHKTGL1WilUkyN31MLoEKOCrFKAYikA6kkEaryQCE%2B8%3D&h=db46e697\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1503483-20200118.htm&h=359b77d9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1503483-20200118.htm</a>"},{"pid":"83591f2bbee762bf9bc88ff7abf6ed8c88160873","tid":1828535,"uid":105773,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T03:00:48.000Z","msg":"係咪on9"},{"pid":"f65679da032a6b46b54dacb4376fa1c027777126","tid":1828535,"uid":62721,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T03:04:06.000Z","msg":"佢話唔係,即=係<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2eb91bf4ef5640b2c413ca7c96071c274e989fe6","tid":1828535,"uid":25601,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T03:07:22.000Z","msg":"扑野個時屋企人聽到係咪"},{"pid":"fd52fd10da64e4f64c7b03a71e4c06886f5f6510","tid":1828535,"uid":268094,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T03:14:13.000Z","msg":"屌你老味 五個成年人逼